OL,3,CWhere can you see the Northern Lights
OL,4,Ctonight?
OL,6,FThe Northern Lights dazzled huge
OL,7,Fswaths of the UK overnight thanks to
OL,8,Fan "extreme" geomagnetic storm.
OL,10,FThe Aurora Borealis was best visible
OL,11,Fin Whitley Bay on the north east
OL,12,Fcoast, Essex, Cambridgeshire and
OL,13,FWokingham in Berkshire.
OL,15,FIt was also spotted in Suffolk, Kent,
OL,16,FHampshire and Liverpool, and was even
OL,17,Fvisible in parts of London.
OL,19,FSo can you spot them tonight if you
OL,20,Fmissed out on Friday?
