OL,6,FWhere can you see the Northern Lights
OL,7,Ftonight?
OL,9,FMet Office spokesperson Stephen Dixon
OL,10,Fsaid the conditions that allowed the
OL,11,FNorthern Lights to appear on Friday
OL,12,Fnight could be replicated on Saturday,
OL,13,Fbut that the exact location was still
OL,14,Funknown.
OL,16,F"We still have to work out some
OL,17,Fdetails on where exactly that will
OL,18,Fbe," Mr Dixon said.
