OL,3,CWhere can you see the Northern Lights
OL,4,Ctonight?
OL,6,FThe colours are determined by the type
OL,7,Fof gas particles involved and the
OL,8,Faltitude at which the collisions occur.
OL,10,FGreens appear due to interactions with
OL,11,Foxygen, red is from oxygen in the
OL,12,Fupper atmosphere while blues and
OL,13,Fpurples are due to the interaction of
OL,14,Fnitrogen.
